OL,3,CMan behind Mike's Carpets dies age 79
OL,5,FAfter a fire closed Leeds Market
OL,6,Ftemporarily in the 1970s Mike expanded
OL,7,Fhis business and at its height had 13
OL,8,Foutlets across the region.
OL,10,FHe finally quit the carpet trade eight
OL,11,Fyears ago to concentrate on a
OL,12,Fsuccessful property portfolio.
OL,14,FHis widow Carol, 60, said Mike was a
OL,15,F"wonderful man".
OL,17,F"Everyone knew him - he was so
OL,18,Fpopular. There'll never be anyone like
OL,19,Fhim," she said.
