OL,3,CMan behind Mike's Carpets dies age 79
OL,5,FCarol said Mike had suffered heart
OL,6,Ffailure, a condition he had lived with
OL,7,Ffor six months.
OL,9,FShe added that his family, including
OL,10,Ftwo children and three grandchildren
OL,11,Fwere buoyed by the support they had
OL,12,Freceived since Mike's death on Tuesday.
